Quality-adjusted survival in patients with metastatic colorectal cancer treated 
with fruquintinib in the FRESCO trial.

Qin S(1), Li J(2), Bai Y(3), Deng Y(4), Yang L(5), Xu RH(6), Zhong H(7), Chen 
