prevalence of SCA/SCD in pregnant women among ethnic tribal populations from 
India.Conclusion: This review article is focused on the effects of SCA/SCD on 
pregnancy outcomes, the consistent follow-up, routine check-ups and successful 
management of complications throughout pregnancy, the various diagnostic methods 
toward preventive methods, curative and management therapeutic strategies and 
also defines the perinatal and maternal outcomes in the ethnic tribal 
populations of India.

